===Interjection===
'''owie!'''
#Same as [[ow]].

===Noun===
'''owie''' ([[owies]])
#(''American, Regional''): A painful, usually minor, injury.
#*'''1997''': If it's an "'''owie'''" that has the child upset, check him from head to toe for injuries. — K. D. Kuch, ''The Babysitter's Handbook'' (Random House 1997, p. 58)

====Usage note====
The interjection is most often used by a child or someone imitating a child.